  {
    label: 'Your booking and payments stay yours',
    value:
      'Square, your scheduler, your POS all keep running. The quote hands off to a text or your booking link, with an optional Stripe deposit to hold the slot.',
  },
  {
    label: 'Every quote in one dashboard',
    value:
      'Finished or abandoned, each quote lands with the vehicle, services, and add-ons the customer picked — so follow-up isn’t a phone-tag exercise.',
  },
  {
    label: 'Tracking baked in',
    value:
      'Step-by-step analytics show where customers drop off and which ads bring booked work — so you scale what converts and kill what doesn’t.',
