    q: 'How much does a detailing website with a quote system cost?',
    a: "Six tiers, install-only — $997–$2,497 to add the wizard to your current site (Form line) or $1,497–$4,497 for a new site with the wizard built in (Website line). No required monthly on any tier. You own everything at handoff; cancel anytime and the site keeps running.",
  },
  {
    q: 'Do I need a new website, or can you just add the wizard to mine?',
    a: "Either works — your call. If your current site is fine, the Form line ($997–$2,497 install) drops the wizard onto it. If you need a new site too, the Website line ($1,497–$4,497 install) builds the system in. Same wizard, same ownership either way.",
  },
  {
    q: 'Is there a monthly fee?',
    a: "No required monthly. You own your site outright — code, repo, domain — and it keeps running whether you pay us anything ongoing or not. Optional support plans are available if you'd rather not manage hosting and updates yourself.",
